Johannesburg- Valentine’s day is a day for commemorating love and for media personality, Lasizwe Dambuza, it was about celebrating self-love. Taking to his social media, Lasizwe shared a video where he shows how he spent his Valentine’s alone. “How you love yourself subsequently teaches others how you want to be loved.
I’ve realized, one does not need a man to find happiness.” Happiness can be found in oneself. Beautifully so, I spent Valentine’s Day alone. Self-love is not selfish,” he wrote.  For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.